'''肛門性交'''（{{lang-en|Anal intercourse}}），简称'''肛交'''，一般是指將勃起的陰莖與人類的肛門或直腸互相接合並彼此摩擦的過程，主要目的是為了令自身獲得性快感<ref name="Weiten">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=09S5DQAAQBAJ&pg=PA349|publisher=Cengage Learning|date=2016-12-05|title=Psychology Applied to Modern Life: Adjustment in the 21st Century|isbn=978-1-305-96847-9|language=en|first=Wayne|last=Weiten|first2=Dana S.|last2=Dunn|first3=Elizabeth Yost|last3=Hammer|page=349|quote=Anal intercourse involves insertion of the penis into a partner's anus and rectum.}}</ref><ref name="Carroll">See [https://books.google.com/?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA271 pages 270–271] for anal sex information, and [https://books.google.com/?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA118 page 118] for information about the clitoris. {{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Sexuality Now: Embracing Diversity|isbn=978-0-495-60274-3|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2009|pages=629 pages|accessdate=2010-12-19|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C}}</ref><ref name="WebMD">{{cite web|title=Anal Sex Safety and Health Concerns|url=http://www.webmd.com/sex/anal-sex-health-concerns|accessdate=2013-08-19|publisher=WebMD|dead-url=no|quote=Often referred to simply as anal sex, anal intercourse is sexual activity that involves inserting the penis into the anus.|archive-date=2017-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112202705/https://www.webmd.com/sex/anal-sex-health-concerns}}</ref>。 其他形式的肛交包括以[[假阴茎|假阴茎]]、[[假陰莖肛交|捆绑式假阴茎]]、[[指交|手指]]或其他物品插入肛门，或以[[舔肛|口、舌对肛门]]进行的[[性刺激|性刺激]]活动<ref name="Answer">{{cite book|author=Barry R. Komisaruk|author2=Beverly Whipple|author3=Sara Nasserzadeh|author4=Carlos Beyer-Flores|title=The Orgasm Answer Guide|isbn=978-0-8018-9396-4|publisher=[[約翰斯·霍普金斯大學出版社|JHU Press]]|year=2009|pages=108–109|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Kkts3AX9QVAC&pg=PA108|archive-date=2013-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527225743/http://books.google.com/books?id=Kkts3AX9QVAC&pg=PA108|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LeRoy">{{cite book| author = Vern LeRoy Bullough| author2 = Bonnie Bullough|title=Human Sexuality: An Encyclopedia|isbn = 0824079728|publisher=Taylor & Francis|year=1994|pages=27–28|accessdate=2013-07-05|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=y5HFtMkmFMYC&pg=PA27}}</ref>。雖然肛交一詞最常用於表示陰莖－肛交<ref name="WebMD"/><ref name="Answer"/><ref name="McBride and Fortenberry">{{Cite journal|title=Heterosexual Anal Sexuality and Anal Sex Behaviors: A Review|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00224490903402538|last=McBride|first=Kimberly R.|last2=Fortenberry|first2=J. Dennis|date=2010-03-24|journal=[[性研究期刊|Journal of Sex Research]]|issue=2-3|doi=10.1080/00224490903402538|volume=47|pages=123–136|language=en|issn=0022-4499|pmid=20358456}}</ref>，但文獻有時會以「Anal intercourse」（肛門性交）去特指陰莖－肛交；「Anal sex」（肛門性愛）則用於表示任何涉及肛門的[[人类性行为|性活動]]，特別是伴侣之間的<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry" /><ref name="Discovery.com">{{cite web|title=Anal Sex, defined|url=http://health.discovery.com/centers/sex/sexpedia/analsex.html|accessdate=2013-07-23|publisher=[[探索頻道|Discovery.com]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020613200634/http://health.discovery.com/centers/sex/sexpedia/analsex.html|archivedate=2002-06-13}}</ref>，而較少用於代表肛門自慰。

雖然一般人通常會將肛交跟男同性戀者扯上關係，但研究表明並非所有同性戀男性都會從事肛交，且它在異性伴侶當中並不罕見<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Not all">{{cite web|title=Not all gay men have anal sex|publisher=Go Ask Alice!|date=2008-06-13|accessdate=2010-04-26|url=http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/not-all-gay-men-have-anal-sex|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706220546/http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/not-all-gay-men-have-anal-sex|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Wellings">{{cite book|author=Kaye Wellings|author2=Kirstin Mitchell|author3=Martine Collumbien|title=Sexual Health: A Public Health Perspective|isbn=0335244815|publisher=McGraw-Hill International|year=2012|page=91|accessdate=2013-08-29|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZKveuj7dLd4C&pg=PA91|archive-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326183233/http://books.google.com/books?id=ZKveuj7dLd4C&pg=PA91|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女同性伴侣亦可能会進行肛交<ref name="Newman">{{cite book|author=Felice Newman|title=The Whole Lesbian Sex Book: A Passionate Guide For All Of Us|isbn = 978-1-57344-199-5|publisher=Cleis Press|year=2004|pages=205–224|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OquFdu3Qt9sC&pg=PA205}}</ref>。人們可通過刺激位於肛門的[[神經|神經]]末梢來獲取愉悦感，並能以插入肛門的方式來達至性高潮：這能間接刺激男性的[[前列腺|前列腺]]、女性陰道的一處區域（其有時稱為[[G點|G點]]）或陰蒂，以及其他感覺神經（特别是[[陰部神經|陰部神經]]）<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Answer"/><ref name="Rosenthal">{{cite book|first=Martha|last=Rosenthal|title=Human Sexuality: From Cells to Society|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2012|pages=133–135|accessdate=2012-09-17|isbn=978-0-618-75571-4|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520211405/https://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT153|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而人們也可能會在過程中感到輕微以至劇烈的痛楚<ref name="Anal Pain">{{cite web|title=Pain from anal sex, and how to prevent it|url=http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/pain-anal-sex-and-how-prevent-it|accessdate=2011-04-07|date=2009-06-26|publisher=Go Ask Alice!|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2015-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150811153612/http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/pain-anal-sex-and-how-prevent-it}}</ref><ref name="Heidelbaugh">{{cite book|title=Clinical men's health: evidence in practice|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|year=2007|page=273|accessdate=2011-10-14|url=https://books.google.com/?id=4N_6nOH5BAEC&pg=PA273|author=Joel J. Heidelbaugh|isbn=978-1-4160-3000-3}}</ref>；某些情況下所產生的痛楚主要是[[心因性|心因性]]的<ref name="Heidelbaugh" />。

與大多數性活動一樣，肛交從事者亦有從中感染性傳播疾病的風險。由於肛門和直腸相對容易受損的關係，所以肛交遭認定為一種高風險的性行為。肛門和直腸組織是十分脆弱的，且不會像陰道般分泌[[陰道分泌液|潤滑液]]，因此它們相對較容易受损，特別是在不使用[[人体润滑剂|人体润滑剂]]的情況下<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="WebMD" /><ref name="Krasner">{{cite book |author=Robert I Krasner| title =The Microbial Challenge: Science, Disease and Public Health| publisher =Jones & Bartlett Publishers|year = 2010|pages=416–417|accessdate=2013-08-28|isbn=0763797359|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nThtlYxP84QC&pg=PA416}}</ref>。沒有安全套保護的肛交是最高風險的性行為<ref name="Krasner"/><ref name="Hales">{{Cite book|author=Dianne Hales|title=An Invitation to Health Brief 2010-2011|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2008|accessdate=2013-08-29|pages=269–271|isbn=0495391921|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oP91HVIMPRIC&pg=PA269|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143640/http://books.google.com/books?id=oP91HVIMPRIC&pg=PA269|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Werner">{{cite book |author=Werner W. K. Hoeger|author2=Sharon A. Hoeger|title=Lifetime Fitness and Wellness: A Personalized Program|publisher =Cengage Learning|year = 2010|page=455|accessdate = 2013-08-28|isbn=1133008585|url =https://books.google.com/books?id=0aw8AAAAQBAJ&pg=PA455}}</ref>，因此像[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]（WHO）般的保健机构建議應在肛交前以及過程中採取[[安全性行為|預防措施]]<ref name="Who">World Health Organization, Department of Reproductive Health and Research [http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2007/9789241563475_eng.pdf Global strategy for the prevention and control of sexually transmitted infections: 2006–2015. Breaking the chain of transmission] {{Wayback|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2007/9789241563475_eng.pdf|date=20140323122753}}, 2007, {{ISBN|978-92-4-156347-5}}</ref>。

肛交在不同的文化及社會中是带有爭議性的，一些宗教禁令会禁止男性從事肛交，或只認可为了[[繁殖|繁殖]]下一代而進行的性活動<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Discovery.com"/>。它亦可能遭某些文化認定為[[禁忌|禁忌]]或違反自然。在一些國家甚至視之為刑事[[犯罪|犯罪]]，肛交者可處以[[體罰|體罰]]或[[死刑|死刑]]。與此相反，一些人認為肛交是一種自然且正当的性行為，可以像其他性活動一樣使人感到满足，並將其看成增强性滿意度的重要元素，甚至視其為他們最主要的性活動<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Discovery.com"/>。
