== 概要与原理 ==
[[File:Male_anatomy_zh.svg|thumb]]
由於位於肛門和[[直腸|直腸]]的[[神經|神經末梢]]相對較為密集的關係，使得不論男女，都能體會到肛交所帶來的愉悅感<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Answer"/><ref name="LeRoy"/>，控制肛門的外[[括约肌|括约肌]]和{{link-en|內括约肌|Internal anal sphincter}}都是敏感的膜質肌，並包含許多神經末梢。這些神經末梢使得人類在肛交过程中感到愉悦或痛楚<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="LeRoy"/>。《人类性百科》（The Human Sexuality: An Encyclopedia）指出：「與肛管的外2/3處比較，內1/3處的敏感度相對較差，但卻對壓力更為敏感……直腸是一條約8-9英寸（大約等於20.32-22.86厘米）長的彎管，且具有像肛門般的擴張力<ref name="LeRoy"/>。」

研究表明，肛交的發生率遠少於其他性行為，但由於其跟「[[支配与臣服|支配与臣服]]」以至[[禁忌|社会禁忌]]有关<ref name="Weiten" />，使得它對不同[[性傾向|性傾向]]者而言，都是一種能為心理帶來刺激的性行為<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Understanding">{{cite book|author =Joann S. DeLora|author2 =Carol A. B. Warren|author3 =Carol Rinkleib Ellison|title=Understanding Sexual Interaction|isbn = 978-0-395-29724-7 |publisher=Houghton Mifflin (Original from the University of Virginia)|origyear=1981 |year=2008|page=123|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lP4cAAAAYAAJ|quote=Many men find anal intercourse more exciting than penile-vaginal intercourse because the anal opening is usually smaller and tighter than the vagina. Probably the forbidden aspect of anal intercourse also makes it more exciting for some people.}}</ref><ref name="dailyuw.com">{{cite web|first=Celia|last=Hunko|title=Anal sex: Let's get to the bottom of this |publisher=''The Daily of the University of Washington''|date=2009-02-06|accessdate=2017-03-11|url=http://dailyuw.com/2009/2/6/anal-sex-lets-get-bottom/|archiveurl=https://archive.li/20100428073805/http://dailyuw.com/2009/2/6/anal-sex-lets-get-bottom/|archivedate=2010-04-28}}</ref>。肛門除了可跟阴茎[[插入式性行為|接合]]以外，还可插入像[[肛門塞|肛門塞]]和[[拉珠|拉珠]]般的[[性玩具|性玩具]]來進行性刺激。其他形式的肛交還包括[[指交|指交]]、[[舔肛|舔肛]]、[[假陰莖肛交|假陰莖肛交]]、{{link-en|肛門自慰|anal masturbation}}，以及[[拳交|拳交]]。肛交的[[性体位|性体位]]亦有許多不同的變化<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Hawley">{{cite book|first=John C|last=Hawley|title=LGBTQ America Today: An Encyclopedia, Volume 1|publisher=Greenwood Press|year=2008|page=977|accessdate=2013-07-05|isbn=0313339902|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MUIOAQAAMAAJ}}</ref>。拳交是當中最為少人實踐的<ref name="Zdrok">{{cite book |first=Victoria|last=Zdrok| title = The Anatomy of Pleasure | publisher =Infinity Publishing|year = 2004|pages=100–102|accessdate = 2013-07-05| isbn = 0741422484 |url =https://books.google.com/books?id=Cx62zwSwbcsC&pg=PA100}}</ref>，部分原因在于只有少數人能把肛門放鬆至容納像拳頭般的物體<ref name="LeRoy"/>。

對於男性容納方而言，伴侶的陰莖在過程中會對他的肛門及直腸壁進行磨擦，令他的[[前列腺|前列腺]]（其有時稱為「男性的G點」）受到間接刺激，這有機會導致愉悦感產生，甚至使当事人達至高潮<ref name="Answer"/><ref name="Rosenthal" />。刺激前列腺可以產生「更強」的性高潮，一些男性認為由此一方式引起的高潮「更瀰漫全身，更強更持久，並且比起僅由刺激陰莖引起的性高潮更為使人歡快<ref name="Answer"/><ref name="Rosenthal" />。」男性前列腺位於直腸旁邊，且跟較不發達的女性[[斯基恩氏腺|斯基恩氏腺]]屬同源<ref name="Lentz">{{cite book|author=Gretchen M Lentz|author2=Rogerio A. Lobo|author3=David M Gershenson|author4=Vern L. Katz|title=Comprehensive Gynecology|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|year=2012|accessdate=2015-03-09|page=41|isbn=0323091318|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=X5KT_w6Nye8C&pg=PA41}}</ref>。雖感覺不盡相同，但透過刺激陰莖引起的男性性高潮亦以前列腺為核心<ref name="Lewin, Leap">{{cite book|author=Ellen Lewin|author2=William Leap|author3=William L. Leap|title=Out in Theory: The Emergence of Lesbian and Gay Anthropology|isbn =0252070763|publisher=University of Illinois Press|year=2002|pages=215–216|accessdate=2013-12-22|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=S02nNWBC3bMC&pg=PA215}}</ref>。男性容納方不能只透過肛交來達至高潮的情況仍是十分普遍<ref name="W. Ross">{{cite book|author=Michael W. Ross|title=Psychopathology and Psychotherapy in Homosexuality|isbn =0866564993|publisher=Psychology Press|year=1988|pages=49–50|accessdate=2013-12-22|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DWN2-QpbvY8C&pg=PA50}}</ref>。

一般統計表明，70-80％的女性都需以直接刺激陰蒂的方式來達至高潮<ref name="Rosenthal" /><ref name="Flaherty">{{cite book|author=Joseph A. Flaherty|author2=John Marcell Davis|author3=Philip G. Janicak|title=Psychiatry: Diagnosis & therapy. A Lange clinical manual|url=https://archive.org/details/psychiatrydiagno00flah|isbn = 978-0-8385-1267-8|publisher=Appleton & Lange (Original from Northwestern University)|date=1993|page=[https://archive.org/details/psychiatrydiagno00flah/page/217 217]|quote=The amount of time of sexual arousal needed to reach orgasm is variable — and usually much longer — in women than in men; thus, only 20–30% of women attain a coital climax. b. Many women (70–80%) require manual clitoral stimulation...}}</ref><ref name="Kammerer-Doak">{{cite journal | first = Dorothy | last = Kammerer-Doak | first2 = Rebecca G. | last2 = Rogers | title = Female Sexual Function and Dysfunction | journal = Obstetrics and Gynecology Clinics of North America | volume = 35 | issue = 2 | pages = 169–183 | doi = 10.1016/j.ogc.2008.03.006 |date=June 2008 | pmid = 18486835  | url = http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ogc.2008.03.006 | quote=Most women report the inability to achieve orgasm with vaginal intercourse and require direct clitoral stimulation ... About 20% have coital climaxes...}}</ref>。陰蒂並不只由位於身體表面的[[陰蒂頭|陰蒂頭]]構成。陰蒂/陰蒂頭所擁有的感覺神經末梢多達8,000條<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Di Marino">{{cite book |last=Di Marino |first=Vincent |title=Anatomic Study of the Clitoris and the Bulbo-Clitoral Organ |publisher=Springer|year=2014|page=81|isbn=3319048945|accessdate=2014-09-04|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wKMpBAAAQBAJ}}</ref>；陰蒂包圍着[[陰道|陰道]]和[[尿道|尿道]]，因此其可能跟肛門有著同樣或類似的關係<ref name="O'Connell">{{cite journal |vauthors=O'Connell HE, Sanjeevan KV, Hutson JM |title=Anatomy of the clitoris |journal=The Journal of Urology |volume=174 |issue=4 Pt 1 |pages=1189–95 |date=October 2005 |pmid=16145367 |laysummary=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5013866.stm |laysource=Time for rethink on the clitoris, [[BBC_News|BBC News]] |laydate=11 June 2006 |doi=10.1097/01.ju.0000173639.38898.cd |access-date=2017-06-24 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909192820/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5013866.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相對較敏感的[[阴蒂脚|阴蒂脚]]位於阴蒂的兩側，其會在性喚起中充血<ref name="O'Connell"/><ref name="Yang">{{cite journal | last = Yang | first = Claire J. | last2 = Cold | first2 = Christopher | last3 = Yilmaz | first3 = Ugur | last4=Kenneth | first4=R. Maravilla | title = Sexually responsive vascular tissue of the vulva | journal = BJUI | volume = 97 | issue = 4 | pages = 766–772 | date = April 2006 | pmid = 16536770| doi = 10.1111/j.1464-410X.2005.05961.x | display-authors = 2 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | first = John P. | last = Mulhall  | first2 = Luca | last2 = Incrocci | first3 = Irwin | last3 = Goldstein | first4 = Ray | last4= Rosen |title = Cancer and Sexual Health | isbn = 978-1-60761-915-4 | publisher = Springer | year = 2011 | page=783 | accessdate = 2012-06-23 | url = https://books.google.com/?id=GpIadil3YsQC&pg=PA13}}</ref>。肛交除了会刺激位於肛門和直腸內的神經末梢之外，還可能會使阴蒂脚受到間接刺激，繼使女性感到愉悅<ref name="Doin' the butt">{{cite web|title=Doin' the butt – objects in anus? |publisher=Go Ask Alice! |date=2010-03-26 |accessdate=2010-04-22 |url=http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/doin-butt-objects-anus |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118005301/http://goaskalice.columbia.edu/doin-butt-objects-anus |archivedate=2012-01-18 }}</ref>。肛門侵入会對陰蒂構成間接刺激的原因亦可能在於兩者之間的感覺神經是共享的，尤其是[[陰部神經|陰部神經]]，陰部神經在陰部管內會分支，先分支為{{le|內直腸神經|inferior anal nerve}}，之後是[[會陰神經|會陰神經]]，最後是{{le|陰蒂背神經|Dorsal nerve of the clitoris|陰蒂的背神經}}<ref name="Answer"/>。

在女性解剖學上，[[G点|G点]]是一處帶有爭議的區域，相關的爭議在醫師和研究者之間尤其激烈<ref name="Sex and Society">{{cite book|author=Marshall Cavendish Corporation|title=Sex and Society, Volume 2|isbn =978-0-7614-7907-9|publisher=Marshall Cavendish Corporation|year=2009|page=590|accessdate=2012-08-17|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YtsxeWE7VD0C&pg=PA590}}</ref><ref name="Greenberg">{{cite book|author=Jerrold S. Greenberg|author2=Clint E. Bruess|author3=Sara B. Oswalt|title=Exploring the Dimensions of Human Sexuality|pages=102–104|isbn=1449648517|date=2014|accessdate=2014-10-30|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hm3aTuANFroC&pg=PA102}}</ref><ref name="Kilchevsky">{{cite journal|title=Is the Female G-Spot Truly a Distinct Anatomic Entity?|journal=The Journal of Sexual Medicine|volume=9|date=January 2012|pmid=22240236|doi=10.1111/j.1743-6109.2011.02623.x|laysummary=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/01/19/g-spot-does-not-exist_n_1215822.html|laysource=G-Spot Does Not Exist, 'Without A Doubt,' Say Researchers - ''[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]''|laydate=19 January 2012|vauthors=Kilchevsky A, Vardi Y, Lowenstein L, Gruenwald I|issue=3|pages=719–26|access-date=2017-06-25|archive-date=2019-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190310161629/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/01/19/g-spot-does-not-exist_n_1215822.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但一般認為其位於陰道前壁上方，它和陰道的其他區域一同遭認為擁有與陰蒂連接的組織和神經<ref name="O'Connell"/><ref name="Sex and Society"/><ref name="Kilchevsky"/>。由於陰道腔和直腸腔之間非常接近的缘故，因此除了可透過「感覺神經共享」此一特點來獲得高潮之外，還可透過對陰蒂或G點區域進行間接刺激，來使從事肛交的女性達至高潮<ref name="Zdrok"/><ref name="Taormino">See [https://books.google.com/books?id=bG8XqRO6rRQC&pg=PA3 page 3] for women preferring anal sex to vaginal sex, and [https://books.google.com/books?id=bG8XqRO6rRQC&pg=PA15 page 15] for reaching orgasm through indirect stimulation of the G-spot. {{cite book|author=Tristan Taormino|title=The Ultimate Guide to Anal Sex for Women|isbn = 978-1-57344-221-3|publisher=Cleis Press|year=1997|pages=282 pages|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hLv1ohTIiicC}}</ref>。能做到只由刺激肛門來達至高潮的女性十分罕見<ref name="Tarrant">{{cite book|author=Shira Tarrant|title=Politics: In the Streets and Between the Sheets in the 21st Century|isbn =1317814754|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|year=2015|pages=247-248|accessdate=2017-03-11|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=t6nwCQAAQBAJ&pg=PT247}}</ref><ref name="Valdez">{{cite book|author =Natasha Janina Valdez|title=Vitamin O: Why Orgasms Are Vital to a Woman's Health and Happiness, and How to Have Them Every Time!|isbn = 978-1-61608-311-3|publisher=Skyhorse Publishing Inc.|year=2011|page=79|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5PsNKTB87isC&pg=PT79}}</ref>。在肛交的同時直接刺激陰蒂和/或G點可使一些女性更為享受，並以此達到高潮<ref name="Carroll"/><ref name="Taormino"/>。

肛交所帶來的刺激感還可能受到當時流行的觀感或印象的影響，比如[[情色|情色]]和[[色情|色情]]作品。肛交通常會被色情作品描繪成不需要[[人体润滑剂|人体润滑剂]]即可無痛地進行的一件事情，這可能會使某些伴侣在肛交时不採取任何的潤滑和預防措施，並導致一些人誤以為如果女性是肛交過程中的容納方，則不應該感到痛苦或不舒服，而是感到非常地愉悅<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/><ref name="Crooks">See [https://books.google.com/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA560 page 560] for effects of viewing pornography with regard to anal sex, and [https://books.google.com/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA286 pages 286–289] for anal sex as a birth control method. {{cite book | title = Our Sexuality | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2010–2011 | pages = 570 pages | accessdate = 2013-05-07 |isbn = 0495812943| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC |author1=Robert Crooks |author2=Karla Baur }}</ref><ref name="Boyle">{{Citation |last= Flood | first = Michael | contribution = Young men using pornography | editor-last = Boyle | editor-first = Karen  | title = Everyday pornography | pages = 170–171 | publisher = Routledge | location = London New York | year = 2010 | isbn = 9780415543781 | ref = harv | postscript = .}} [http://www.xyonline.net/sites/default/files/Flood,%20Young%20men%20using%20porn.pdf Pdf.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020075102/http://www.xyonline.net/sites/default/files/Flood%2C%20Young%20men%20using%20porn.pdf |date=2016-10-20 }} [https://books.google.com/books?id=8yznvRX-hfAC&pg=PA170 Preview.]</ref><ref name="Johansson">{{cite book | title = The Transformation of Sexuality: Gender And Identity In Contemporary Youth Culture | publisher = Ashgate Publishing | year = 2007 | pages = 56–58 | accessdate = 2013-05-07 |isbn = 1409490785| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=XPm3JEiunnsC&pg=PA56| author = Thomas Johansson}}</ref>。與以上觀點相反，每個人的括約肌肌肉對性侵入的反應都有點不同，肛門括約肌的某些組織較容易受損，且肛門和直腸不會像陰道般分泌潤滑液。研究者們認為，就避免肛門或直腸疼痛此一層面而言，相對較為重要的措施是充分利用人体润滑剂、放鬆自己，以及多跟伴侣溝通<ref name="Carroll" /><ref name="Heidelbaugh"/><ref name="lubrication">{{Cite journal|last1= Carballo-Diéguez|first1= Alex|last2= Stein|first2= Z.|year= 2000|title= Frequent use of lubricants for anal sex among men who have sex with men|journal= American Journal of Public Health|volume= 90|issue= 7|pages= 1117–1121|url= http://www.ajph.org/cgi/reprint/90/7/1117.pdf|doi= 10.2105/AJPH.90.7.1117|last3= Saez|first3= H.|last4= Dolezal|first4= C.|last5= Nieves-Rosa|first5= L.|last6= Diaz|first6= F.|pmid= 10897191|pmc= 1446289|author= |access-date= 2017-06-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080920180128/http://www.ajph.org/cgi/reprint/90/7/1117.pdf|archive-date= 2008-09-20|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。此外為了回應伴侣的期望，肛交過程中的容納方可能需確保肛門以及直腸的洁净程度<ref name="Zdrok"/>。

== 同性之間的肛交 ==
===男對男===
{{main|攻受}}
[[File:Édouard-Henri_Avril_(18).jpg|thumb]]画作《在埃及的[[哈德良|哈德良]]与[[安提诺乌斯|安提诺乌斯]]》男对男肛交]]
人們通常認爲肛交與[[同性戀|同性戀]]有關，但是許多男男性接觸者和男同性戀者一般不會從事肛交<ref name="Not all"/><ref name="Wellings"/><ref name="Johnson and Johnson">{{cite book|title=Gay Perspective: Things Our Homosexuality Tells Us about the Nature of God & the Universe|isbn=978-1-59021-015-4|publisher=Lethe Press|year=2008|page=139|accessdate=2011-02-12|url=https://books.google.com/?id=LPyhsuVbUlAC&pg=PA139|author=Edwin Clark Johnson|author2=Toby Johnson}}</ref><ref name="Goldstone">{{cite journal|title=Sexually Transmitted Diseases of the Colon, Rectum, and Anus|first1=Stephen E.|last2=Welton|first2=Mark L.|journal=Clin Colon Rectal Surg|issue=4|doi=10.1055/s-2004-836944|year=2004|volume=17|pages=235–239|pmc=2780055|pmid=20011265|last1=Goldstone}}</ref>。在男男肛交者當中，插入陰莖者可稱為「1號」（英語稱為top<ref name="Underwood">{{cite book | author =Steven Gregory Underwood|title =Gay Men and Anal Eroticism: Tops, Bottoms, and Versatiles|isbn = 978-1-56023-375-6 |publisher=Harrington Park Press|year=2003|pages=4–225|accessdate=2011-02-12|url=https://books.google.com/?id=i4wRl0_8NuUC&pg=PA4}}</ref><ref name="urban Peru">[http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Role+versatility+among+men+who+have+sex+with+men+in+urban+Peru.-a0168586762] Role versatility among men who have sex with men in urban Peru. In: ''The Journal of Sex Research'', August 2007</ref>），容納者則可稱為「0號」（英語稱為「bottom」<ref name="Underwood"/><ref name="urban Peru" /><ref>{{cite book|title=中國同性愛史錄|author=小明雄|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=oFhxAAAAIAAJ&q=肛交+1+0&dq=肛交+1+0&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&redir_esc=y|publisher=粉紅三角出版社|year=1997|page=491|isbn=9789628516018|accessdate=2017-07-04}}</ref>），兼具1和0的特点的可稱為「0.5號」<ref>{{cite web|title=同性恋专有名词解释|publisher=中华心理教育网|url=http://www.xinli110.com/xing/TXZA/YXJS/201012/194747.html|date=2010-12-16|accessdate=2017-07-04|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521005759/http://www.xinli110.com/xing/TXZA/YXJS/201012/194747.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>（英語稱為「versatile」<ref name="Underwood"/><ref name="urban Peru" />）。在日式BL漫画、小说中耽美、BL文化的专用名词“攻”（1号）、“受”（0号）更加常用，但夹带了对性別气质的描述<ref>{{cite news |author=張碧尤|title=【腐女想甚麼？】BL漫畫「攻」「受」關係滿足女讀者情慾想像 |url=https://www.hk01.com/好生活/38159/腐女想甚麼-bl漫畫-攻-受-關係滿足女讀者情慾想像 |publisher=香港01|date=2016-08-18|accessdate=2018-12-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=陆国静 |title=耽美文化及同人女群体研究 |date=2011-04-12 |page=19 |url=http://kns.cnki.net/kcms/detail/Detail.aspx?dbname=CMFD2012&filename=1012583025.nh&v=&filetitle=%E8%80%BD%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A5%B3%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6 |accessdate=2018-12-20 |publisher=苏州大学}}</ref>。

喜歡肛交的男同性戀者可能視它等同於異性戀者的性交，並視之為一種自然的親密表達——利用其來取悅自身的伴侶，以及表達好感<ref name="dailyuw.com"/><ref name="Johnson and Johnson"/><ref name="Smith">{{cite book|title=Encyclopedia of AIDS: A Social, Political, Cultural and Scientific Record of the HIV Epidemic|author=Raymond A. Smith|publisher=Taylor & Francis|year=1998|pages=73–76|isbn=0203305493|accessdate=2013-12-23|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vuAWLtgnUm0C&pg=PA73}}</ref>。有學者認為它對於男同性戀者的情感意義跟異性戀者的陰道性交一樣<ref name="Smith" /><ref name="Advocate.com">{{cite news|title=The New Sex Police|work=The Advocate|date=2005-04-12|accessdate=2011-02-12|pages=39–40, 42|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mGMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA39|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919005938/https://books.google.com/books?id=mGMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA39|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但亦有一些男男性接觸者相信，在肛交期間扮演容纳方即代表自身的[[男性气质|男性氣質]]遭到質疑<ref name="Harvey, Wenzel, and Sprecher">{{cite book |author1=John H. Harvey |author2=Amy Wenzel |author3=Susan Sprecher |title =The handbook of sexuality in close relationships|isbn = 0805845488|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|year=2004|pages=355–356|accessdate=2011-03-12|url=https://books.google.com/?id=qsl4AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA355}}</ref><ref name="Odets">{{cite book|first=Walt|last=Odets|title=In the Shadow of the Epidemic: Being Hiv-negative in the Age of AIDS|publisher=Duke University Press|year=1995|pages=191–192|accessdate=2013-07-06|isbn=0822316382|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9nokfyi64GwC&pg=PA191|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918185610/https://books.google.com/books?id=9nokfyi64GwC&pg=PA191|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一些男男性接觸者会更願意從事[[陰莖摩擦|陰莖摩擦]]或[[自慰#互相抚慰|互相撫慰]]，因為他們認為以上兩者更加使人愉悦以及更能表達情感，能夠避免失貞（因視肛交的地位等同性交），且相比起肛交更為[[安全性行為|安全]]<ref name="Johnson and Johnson"/><ref name=Underwood/><ref name="Virgin">{{cite book|first=Michael|last=Joseph Gross|title = Like a Virgin|id = 0001-8996|work=The Advocate, Here Publishing|year=2003|pages=44–45|accessdate=2011-03-12|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eWQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA44}}</ref>。另外也有一些主張陰莖摩擦的男男性接觸者對肛交作出批評，認為它會貶低過程中的容納方，並造成不必要的健康風險<ref name="Advocate.com" /><ref name="out.com">{{cite news|first=Tom|last=Dolby|title=Why Some Gay Men Don't Go All The Way|work=Out|date=February 2004|accessdate=2011-02-12|pages=76–77|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jmIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA77}}</ref>。

====盛行率====
男同性戀者和[[男男性行为者|男男性接觸者]]，從事肛交的盛行率數據有着不少差異。關注LGBT議題的美國雜誌《拥护者》曾於1994年就此進行了一項調查。當中發現美國6％的男同性戀者傾向於扮演侵入方，43％則傾向於扮演容納方<ref name="Underwood"/>。其他來源則指出，大約四分之三的美國男同性戀者進行過至少1次的肛交，扮演「0號」和「1號」的比例大致相同<ref name=Underwood/>。2012年美國性健康與行為調查指出，83.3％的男同性戀者曾從事過自身扮演侵入方的肛交，曾扮演容納方的則有90％，但只有四分之一至三分之一的男同性戀者報稱在近期（30天以內）從事過肛交<ref name="dodge">{{cite journal|title=Sexual Behaviors of U.S. Men by Self-Identified Sexual Orientation: Results From the 2012 National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior|author1=Brian Dodge|author2=et al.|year=2016|journal=J Sex Med|volume=13|pages=37e649|doi=10.1016/j.jsxm.2016.01.015}}</ref>。

在男男性接觸者當中，口交和互相撫慰比與刺激肛門相关的性活動更為常見<ref name="Weiten"/><ref name="Johnson and Johnson"/><ref name="Brannon">{{cite book |author =Linda Brannon|title =Gender: Psychological Perspectives, Sixth Edition|isbn =1317348133|publisher=Psychology Press|year=2015|page=484|accessdate=2016-12-10|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qd85CgAAQBAJ&pg=PT484}}</ref>。魏滕（Weiten）等人指出，儘管肛交在男同性戀之中的確較為普遍，但是不論性取向，「它的盛行率都比口交和互相撫慰排得更後<ref name="Weiten" />……將『同性戀者』等同於『男男肛交者』的想法在專業人才和医師之中亦是普遍，但據一項互聯網調查顯示（EMIS，2011），歐洲18萬的男男性接觸者當中，最常會進行的是口交，其次是互相撫慰，肛交則排在第三<ref name="Wellings"/>。」

據潘綏銘於1993年針對中國男同性戀者的調查顯示，48.5％的男同性戀的「肛門曾被他人生殖器插入」（肛交），盛行率同樣低於「口刺激他人的生殖器」（口交）以及「生殖器被觸摸」（手交），上月有過者則為23.6％<ref>{{cite book |author =潘綏銘| publisher=光明日报出版社|title=中国性现状|page=431|year=1995|isbn=9787800916700}}</ref>。2006年的另一項大型調查則顯示，中國85％的男男性接觸者曾從事過肛交<ref>{{cite book |author1 = Siân M. Griffiths|author2 =Jin Ling Tang|author3 = Eng Kiong Yeoh|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=pxRgAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT382&dq=anal+sex+china+MSM&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiF6p2j1fbUAhWMn5QKHSMoD1sQ6AEILDAB#v=onepage&q=anal%20sex%20china%20MSM&f=false|title=Routledge Handbook of Global Public Health in Asia|publisher=Routledge|year=2014|isbn=978-0415643825}}</ref>。

===女對女===
[[Image:Wiki-analoral.png|thumb]]（模擬）]]
就女同性性行為而言，肛交的形式則包括以[[指交|手指]]、像假陰莖般的性玩具，或口舌來刺激肛門<ref name="Newman"/><ref name="Loulan">{{cite book|author =JoAnn Loulan|title =Lesbian Sex|isbn = 0-933216-13-0|publisher=The University of California|date=1984|page=53|accessdate=2011-02-03|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bS0EAQAAIAAJ}}</ref>。一些女同性戀者並不喜歡肛交<ref name="Harding">{{cite book|author=Kat Harding|title=The Lesbian Kama Sutra|isbn = 0-312-33585-7|publisher=Macmillan|year=2006 |page=31|accessdate=2011-02-03|url=https://books.google.com/?id=m5RkdiYYMBMC&pg=PA31}}</ref>，且少有女同性戀者會進行舔肛<ref name="Zenilman & Shahmanesh">{{cite book|title=Sexually Transmitted Infections: Diagnosis, Management, and Treatment|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|year=2011|pages=329–330|accessdate=2012-11-04|isbn=0495812943|url=https://books.google.com/?id=lO5BND02eBwC&pg=PA329|author1=Jonathan Zenilman|author2=Mohsen Shahmanesh}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Lesbians' Sexual Activities and Efforts to Reduce Risks for Sexually Transmitted Diseases|date=Jun 2000|journal=J Gay Lesbian Med Assoc.|issue=2|doi=10.1023/A:1009513623365|volume=4|pages=41–8|vauthors=Diamant AL, Lever J, Schuster M}}</ref>。

與其他性取向人士相比之下，有關[[女女性行为|女女性接觸者]]實行肛交的研究相對較少。1987年，科羅拉多州的一個女同性戀社會組織對該組織的100多名成員進行了一項非科學性研究，當中問及她們過去十次性經歷中所使用的技巧。及後發現與其他年齡組相比，30多歲的女同性戀者有多一倍機會會（以手指或假陰莖）對其伴侶的肛門進行刺激<ref name="Carroll" />。湯姆·博爾斯托夫（Tom Boellstorff）這位著者則表示，他在印度尼西亞調查同性戀者的肛交行為時，虽沒有聽說過女同性戀性行為的常規形式包括口部－肛門接觸或肛門侵入，但仍假設其是有發生過的<ref name="Boellstorff">{{cite book|author =Tom Boellstorff|title=The Gay Archipelago: Sexuality and Nation in Indonesia|isbn = 978-0-691-12334-9 |publisher=Princeton University Press|year=2005|pages=101–102|accessdate=2011-03-12|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Whr4Tb0EuZUC&pg=PA101}}</ref>。另一名著者{{link-en|菲利斯·紐曼|Felice Newman}}則把肛交視為女同性性行為的一部分<ref name="Newman"/>。2014年一項針對加拿大和美國的女同性戀伴侣的研究發現，7％的女同性戀伴侣每周至少一次地從事肛門刺激，每月的則有約10％，從來沒有的亦有70％<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Cohen|first1=Jacqueline N.|last2=Byers|first2=E. Sandra|title=Beyond Lesbian Bed Death: Enhancing Our Understanding of the Sexuality of Sexual-Minority Women in Relationships|journal=JOURNAL OF SEX RESEARCH|date=2014|volume=51|issue=8|pages=893–903|doi=10.1080/00224499.2013.795924|issn=0022-4499}}</ref>。

== 異性之間的肛交 ==
===男對女===
[[File:Anal_Intercourse_Artwork.jpg|thumb]]画作《[[皮埃特罗·阿雷蒂诺|皮埃特罗·阿雷蒂诺]]》男对女肛交]]
肛門括約肌通常比陰道的{{link-en|骨盆肌肉|Pelvic floor}}更為绷紧，這會使得陰莖侵入肛門時所受的壓迫感大大增加，繼使男方的性快感加强<ref name="WebMD"/><ref name="Understanding" /><ref name="Taormino"/>。男方也可因為肛交所帶來的支配感而感到享受，「支配感」是源於肛交時女方的表現、社會禁忌，在某些情況下也可能源於認为自己擁有更多的性行為可供選擇及進行<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Understanding"/>。

雖然一些女性只在取悦男性時才會進行肛交，在肛交期間更會感到痛苦和不舒服，但是亦有不少女性認為它是能為自身帶來愉悅感的一種性活動，對它的熱愛甚至高於[[陰道性交|陰道性交]]<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/><ref name="Taormino"/><ref name="Howe">{{cite book| author = Adrian Howe | title = Sex, Violence and Crime: Foucault and the 'Man' Question| publisher = [[Routledge|Routledge]] | year = 2008 | page = 35 | accessdate = 2013-07-16 |isbn = 0203891279| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=W6aoQfurvT4C&pg=PA35}}</ref><ref name="Alters and Schiff">{{cite book| author = Sandra Alters| author2 = Wendy Schiff | title = Essential Concepts for Healthy Living| publisher =Jones & Bartlett Publishers | year = 2012 | page = 144 | accessdate = 2013-07-16 |isbn = 1449630626| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=VegUiVbruBMC}}</ref>。與陰蒂和肛門相比之下，陰道壁所擁有的神經末梢明顯較少，因此在大多數情況下，刺激陰道所帶來的性快感遠不如直接刺激陰蒂的強烈<ref name="Sex and Society"/><ref name="Kilchevsky"/><ref name="Weiten 2">{{Cite book|author=Wayne Weiten|author2=Dana S. Dunn|author3=Elizabeth Yost Hammer|title=Psychology Applied to Modern Life: Adjustment in the 21st Century|isbn=9781111186630|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2011|page=386|accessdate=2012-01-05|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CGu96TeAZo0C&pg=PT423|archive-date=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614031527/http://books.google.com/books?id=CGu96TeAZo0C&pg=PT423|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但刺激肛門也不一定比刺激陰道更為有效使人達至性高潮——神經的類型以及它們之間的相互作用也是「能否達至性高潮」的關鍵因素<ref name="Answer"/>。

一篇2010年發表的臨床回顧以肛門性交（anal intercourse）去特指陰莖－肛交，肛門性愛（Anal sex）則用於表示任何涉及肛門的性活動。該回顧指出，肛門性愛罕見於一些異性性伴侣的性实践中，但「對於一定數量的異性戀者而言，肛門性愛是非常令人愉悦及興奮的，所帶給人的親密度甚至高於陰道交<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/>。」

肛門性交可以在[[月經|月經]]期間扮演陰道性交的代替品<ref name="LeRoy"/>。因肛交而懷孕的可能性也遠低於陰道性交，因為除非過程中所射出的精子以某種方式進入陰道，否則肛交本身不會導致懷孕。正因為如此，有些伴侣會將肛交視為[[生育控制|生育控制]]的一種方法<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Crooks"/><ref>SIECUS ''Prevalence of Unprotected Anal Sex among Teens Requires New Education Strategies"[https://web.archive.org/web/20171231103438/http://www.sexedlibrary.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=Feature.showFeature&featureid=1036&pageid=682&parentid=478] Accessed January 26, 2010</ref>。

男性對女性進行的肛交常遭視為一种避免失貞的手段，因為它是非生殖性的，且不会導致[[处女膜|处女膜]]破裂。只進行過肛交或其他性行為，而沒有從事過陰道性交的人經常遭異性戀者和研究人員認定为没有失貞，這情況在界定女性失貞與否時特別常見<ref name="Carpenter">See [https://books.google.com/books?id=6qNCeI2AcY4C&pg=PT11 here] and [https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&pg=PA48 pages 48–49] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC&pg=PA48 |date=20161201074430 }} for the majority of researchers and heterosexuals defining virginity loss/"technical virginity" by whether or not a person has engaged in vaginal sex. {{Cite book|author=Laura M. Carpenter|title=Virginity lost: an intimate portrait of first sexual experiences|publisher=NYU Press|year=2005|accessdate=2011-10-09|pages=295 pages|isbn=978-0-8147-1652-6|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pXXZn_qSoDoC}}</ref><ref name="Intimate">{{Cite book|author1=Bryan Strong |author2=Christine DeVault |author3=Theodore F. Cohen |title=The Marriage and Family Experience: Intimate Relationship in a Changing Society| publisher = Cengage Learning|year = 2010|accessdate=2011-10-08 |page = 186| isbn = 0-534-62425-1|url=https://books.google.com/?id=qjvoSOMB5JMC&pg=PA186|quote=Most people agree that we maintain virginity as long as we refrain from sexual (vaginal) intercourse. But occasionally we hear people speak of 'technical virginity' [...] Data indicate that 'a very significant proportion of teens ha[ve] had experience with oral sex, even if they haven't had sexual intercourse, and may think of themselves as virgins' [...] Other research, especially research looking into virginity loss, reports that 35% of virgins, defined as people who have never engaged in vaginal intercourse, have nonetheless engaged in one or more other forms of heterosexual sexual activity (e.g., oral sex, anal sex, or mutual masturbation).}}</ref><ref name="Jayson">{{Cite news|first=Sharon|last=Jayson|title='Technical virginity' becomes part of teens' equation|work=USA Today|date=2005-10-19|accessdate=2009-08-07|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-10-19-teens-technical-virginity_x.htm|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305090437/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-10-19-teens-technical-virginity_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Plummer">{{cite book | author = Ken Plummer | title = Modern Homosexualities: Fragments of Lesbian and Gay Experiences | publisher = [[劳特里奇|Routledge]] | year = 2002 | pages = 187–191 | accessdate = 2013-08-24 | isbn = 1134922426 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=OSO3q4XEfz4C&pg=PA189 | quote = The social construction of 'sex' as vaginal intercourse affects how other forms of sexual activity are evaluated as sexually satisfying or arousing; in some cases whether an activity is seen as a sexual act at all. For example, unless a woman has been penetrated by a man's penis she is still technically a virgin even if she has had lots of sexual experience. | archive-date = 2015-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150318215831/http://books.google.com/books?id=OSO3q4XEfz4C&pg=PA189 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。異性戀者可能將肛交視為前戲或「不该做的事」。勞拉·卡彭特（Laura M. Carpenter）這名學者表示，這種觀點「可追溯到十六世紀末期，明確的『界線』則出現在二十世紀初，其就像婚姻手冊對愛撫的定義一樣：『雖字面上每一個已婚夫婦都知道是抚摸的意思，但不認定其為完整的性交的一部份<ref name="Carpenter"/>。』」

====流行率====
因為大多數關於肛交的研究都聚焦於[[男男性接触人群|男男性接觸者]]，因此有關異性性接觸者肛交的盛行率數據仍是只有很少<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/><ref name="Coleman">{{cite book |authors =Hardin L.K. Coleman, Christine Yeh|title =Handbook of School Counseling|isbn = 1135283591|publisher=[[劳特里奇|Routledge]]|year=2011|page=247|accessdate=2016-12-10|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rBiPAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA247}}</ref>。由金伯利·麥克布萊德（Kimberly R. McBride）於2010年發表的臨床回顧指出，[[社會規範|社會規範]]的變異可能會影響異性肛門性交的頻率。麥克布萊德及其同事調查了1,299名美國男性樣本和1,919名美國女性樣本的肛門性愛盛行率，並將其與肛門性交相比。他們在當中發現51％的男性和43％的女性曾參與過舔肛、肛門指交或使用肛門性玩具至少一次。報告亦指出在過去12個月內有從事異性肛門性交的631名男性和856名女性當中，大多數都是已婚的，已婚者分别佔了69％和73％<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/>。該回顧及後補充道，因為「異性伴侶之間所進行的肛交和其他涉及肛門的性活動相對較少會遭到關注」，所以「將肛門視作性器官的研究是『非常罕見的』。於是結果就是我們不知道肛交與性交之間有多大程度的差異<ref name="McBride and Fortenberry"/>。」

根據2010年的{{link-en|美國性健康與行為調查|National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior}}（NSSHB），與其他性行為相比下，會報稱有從事過肛門性交的女性較為罕見，但18-49歲組的有伴女性有較大可能会報稱在過去90天內有從事過肛門性交至少一次。會從事肛交的女性比男性少。 相比在肛交中扮演插入方，陰道性交在男性當中比較常見。但25-49歲的男性當中有13％-15％在異性肛交中扮演插入方<ref name="Carroll 2">{{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Discovery Series: Human Sexuality|edition=1st|publisher=Cengage Learning|pages=285–286|isbn=1111841896|year=2012|accessdate=2016-12-10|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gU3SZSh-eXsC&pg=PT316|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305140952/https://books.google.com/books?id=gU3SZSh-eXsC&pg=PT316|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nationalsexstudy.indiana.edu/ National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior (NSSHB).] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationalsexstudy.indiana.edu/ |date=20140201060530 }} Findings from the National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior, Center for Sexual Health Promotion, Indiana University. ''The Journal of Sexual Medicine'', Vol. 7, Supplement 5. 2010.</ref>。

有關青年肛交盛行率的數據亦是十分有限。這可能是因為肛交在不少社會中屬於禁忌的關係，使得青年和護理人員都儘量避免對這個議題展開討論。科目評核人員和學校避免討論及教授這個議題的情況亦屬常見。一項發表於2000年的研究發現，在自稱已經有過性行為的美國大學生當中，有22.9％肛交過。而當中只有20.9％的肛交有使用安全套保護，有使用安全套保護的陰道性交則高了一倍，達42.9％<ref name=Coleman/>。

現今異性戀者比以往更普遍地從事肛交，此現象部分可歸因於色情作品的描繪。定期觀看涉及肛門性活動的色情作品的男性更傾向於從事肛交<ref name="Boyle"/><ref name="Johansson"/><ref name="Seidman">{{cite book|title =Introducing the New Sexuality Studies|edition =2nd|author=Steven Seidman|author2=Nancy Fischer|author3=Chet Meeks|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|year=2011|pages=108–112|isbn=1136818103|accessdate=2013-12-22|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2rmjynItoEkC&pg=PA108}}</ref>。塞德曼（Seidman）等人認為：「更多人能夠生產和觀看色情作品的原因在於其愈趨便宜普及，但最大功勞的莫過於互動媒體的誕生。」而這種生產色情作品的方式除了會使臀部和肛門變得更為色情以外，还導致了現今男性對肛交產生極大興趣，以至對其產生一種執著<ref name="Seidman"/>。

據[[潘綏銘|潘綏銘]]等人於2000-2010年（每5年1次調查）進行的中國公民隨機抽樣調查顯示，在調查進行前的过去12个月里，有过性生活且有從事肛門性交的异性恋者從2.8％升至8.5％，共增加5.7％ 。著者認為其仍屬中國社會最禁忌的性技巧<ref name="性之变">{{cite book|title =性之变 21世纪中国人的性生活|author1=潘綏銘|author2=黄盈盈|year=2013|publisher=中国人民大学出版社|isbn=9787300163741}}</ref>{{rp|218-219}}，2015年的調查則顯示相關數字已升至13.8％<ref>{{cite web|title =中国人的性技巧：革命已经成功（发布08）|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102w3q1.html|author=潘綏銘|date=2016-02-05|accessdate=2017-07-28}}</ref>。在已婚且有過婚外性行為者之中，跟別人從事過肛交的比例亦高於跟妻子或丈夫一同從事的。男性有10.2％跟別人從事過肛交，女性則有13.4％；跟妻子或丈夫一同從事肛交的則分别有9.9％和6.6％。但就结論而言，婚外性中使用的其他性技巧都不比婚内更多<ref name="性之变"/>{{rp|311-312}}。

===女對男===
[[File:Wiki-pegging.png|thumb]]
女性除了可用手指來刺激男性肛門的內外，還可以其來刺激[[會陰|會陰]]（男性陰囊與肛門之間）、進行[[前列腺按摩|前列腺按摩]]、以及用口來進行舔肛<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Zdrok"/><ref name="Keesling">{{cite book |first=Barbara|last=Keesling| title = Sexual Pleasure: Reaching New Heights of Sexual Arousal and Intimacy | publisher =Hunter House|year = 2005|page=221|accessdate = 2013-07-06| isbn = 9780897934350 |url =https://books.google.com/books?id=EG2qGvbgneoC}}</ref>。亦可利用像[[假陰莖|假陰莖]]般的性玩具來進行刺激<ref name="LeRoy"/><ref name="Zdrok"/>。女方戴着一條捆綁式假陰莖，並以此跟男方的肛門接入的行為則稱作「[[假陰莖肛交|假陰莖肛交]]」（pegging）<ref name="Hawley"/><ref name="Savage">{{cite web|first=Dan|last=Savage|title=We Have a Winner!|publisher=''The Stranger''|date=2001-06-21|accessdate=2011-07-05|url=http://thestranger.com/seattle/SavageLove?oid=7730}}</ref>。

異性戀男性一般會抵制自身在性行為中扮演容纳方的做法，因為他們認為這種行為過於[[女性化|女性化]]，會令自己變得柔弱，甚至認為它在質疑自己的性傾向<ref name="Zdrok"/><ref name="Odets"/>。但《[[英國醫學期刊|英國醫學期刊]]》於1999年指出：<blockquote>有關「多少處於異性關係中的異性戀男性希望伴侶會對其肛門進行刺激」的數據十分有限。但其實會這樣希望的男性不算少。我們所收集的數據幾乎都是跟性侵入行為有關的，而肛環表面與手指或舌頭接觸的記錄則更為少有，但仍可假定其是男性當中常見的性行為，不論其性取向。<ref name="Robin Bell">{{cite journal|title=ABC of sexual health: Homosexual men and women|last=Bell|first=Robin|date=February 1999|journal=BMJ|publisher=[[國家衛生院_(美國)|National Institutes of Health]]/''BMJ''|issue=7181|doi=10.1136/bmj.318.7181.452|volume=318|pages=452–5|pmc=1114912|pmid=9974466}}</ref></blockquote>

里斯（Reece）等人於2010年指出，整體而言，在肛交中會扮演容纳方的男性並不常見，「14至94歲的男性當中估計有7％在肛交中會扮演容纳方<ref name="Carroll2">{{cite book |author=Janell L. Carroll| title = Discovery Series: Human Sexuality| edition = 1st | publisher = Cengage Learning|page=285| isbn = 1111841896|year=2012| accessdate = 2013-08-25 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gU3SZSh-eXsC&pg=PT317}}</ref>。」

